rows.label: qst201915_msg0001
rows.name:
Yes, yes, we have listened to the
troubles of many of the girls here.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0002
rows.name: Be sure to help them out later.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0004
rows.name:
I mean, everyone's
troubles... how many?

rows.label: qst201915_msg0005
rows.name:
Everyone's troubles...
how many could that be?

rows.label: qst201915_msg0006
rows.name:
Troubles? All of 'em here?!
How many is that...?

rows.label: qst201915_msg0007
rows.name:
You will find out when
you ask them later.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0008
rows.name:
Do not worry. Of course, we will
help too, so rest assured.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0009
rows.name:
No need for hesitation.
Between you and us.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0010
rows.name:
We will help each other
and get along well!

rows.label: qst201915_msg0011
rows.name:
It may be a bit much, but
there should be no problem.

rows.label: qst201915_msg0012
rows.name:
If you are our Driver, you must
have that much capability!
